⁣⁣
What do you think about new game plus? Worthy addition or needless gameplay stretchers?⁣

🎮 PAX AUS: 3 Day Gaming Convention returns to Melbourne on 11 - 13 October, 2019. PAX was a big surprise for us last year. Whilst the event aims to entertain older kids, teens and the adult gamer crowd, our two absolutely loved last year's PAX.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
The three-day convention brings together tens of thousands of like-minded people to celebrate everything they love about gaming.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Our kids really enjoyed meeting up and coming game designers, playing VR games, spotting familiar cosplay characters and trying out tabletop gaming for the first time. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Be aware, PAX does get busy and no prams are allowed (too hectic for prams!) so best get there early if you plan to go. Under 6yrs enter free with a paying adult.⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
PAX Aus is in Melbourne 11 - 13 October 2019 at the Melbourne Convention and Exhibition Centre (MCEC).⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

caption.text:
Akumajou Dracula X: Chi no Rondo, AKA Castlevania: Rondo of blood.

The game was released in japan on oct 29th, 1993. An amazing halloween gift for our Japanese buddies! And it wasn't released outside of Japan for almost 15 years. At some point it was considered the best Castlevania ever, and I think everyone thought alike until Symphony of the Night. So basically, a lost jewell for the western world. There was a remake in the SNES but it was actually a complete different game. It was possible to play it as an unlockable game in The Dracula X Chronicles... But now we are going to be able to enjoy the original game for the first time, on the Turbografx-16 mini!!! So, the first videos are an amazing intro animation. The voice translation is: "Long ago people lived in peace and harmony. No one noticed the looming shadow among them. Their senses clouded in darkness, evil ate away at their souls. In the late hour they congregate to call the powers of Satan with sinful blood to save them from their mortal existence. Evis has once again been made flesh. He can become a bat, fog, or wolf and feasts on human blood. Lord of darkness, master of Castlevania, Dracula walk among us." This game has a fantastic soundtrack, making use of the CD-Rom capacity for better sound quality. There's a 2CD OST released with music from this game and also from Castlevania Bloodlines. Last clip is just a screen I left because of awesome music.

Yo #unicorngang🦄 ....
Man I love Samus Aran. Isn't she one hell of a female heroine? Not over sexualized, no damsel in distress, no men to tell her what she has to do (okay let's ignore Metroid Other M). Just a kick-ass female Bounty Hunter that would wipe the floor with Boba Fett!
And holy moly do I love this wonderful remake of Metroid 2! I would love to see this ported to the Switch since I barely play my 3DS anymore. But for this game I dusted it of and didn't put it down before the credits rolled.

Aaand another resident of Normaltown, and quite a new one too. Meet Dell Van De Laar, a genius mechanic and scientist, living alone with their "family" of androids they created by themself. They separated themself from all other people and work on robots and machines all day. 
Dell's eyes started to fail due to their unhealthy work conditions, so they constructed their own artificial ones to save themself from going blind - and it worked splendid.
Dell's house is basically an impenetrable fortress, surrounded by guarding machines from every side. They don't want any visitors nosing around their property.

Ресурс пишет: «Никаких новостей о втором сезоне «Ведьмака». Тем не менее, по нашим данным некоторое время назад шел подбор актеров для озвучания мультсериала «Ведьмак», в котором появится несколько побочных персонажей [из основного сериала]. План состоял в том, чтобы выпустить его где-то между 1 и 2 сезоном. ⠀

Эту информацию косвенно подтверждает найденное блогом Redanian Intelligence резюме немецкой актрисы Хелены Клаус на сайте Spotlight. Согласно списку ролей, Хелена работает над закадровым озвучанием в «Ведьмаке» и там же упоминается режиссер Ванесса Бейкер, специализирующаяся на озвучании.

Пандария (Анг. Pandaria) ⠀
⠀
Материк, называемый сегодня Пандарией, был южной частью единого Калимдора, пока Война Древних не расколола его.
⠀
Эти земли были местом  сражения Титанов и их слуг, каменных могу, против Древнего Бога И'Шараджа и богомолов.
⠀
Богомолы были побеждены, и титанам удалось убить И'Шараджа, оставив лишь его сердце.
⠀
Прежде чем покинуть Азерот, титаны оставили здесь двух стражей - Норусхена, чтобы охранять сердце, и Ра-дена, чтобы следить за могу, которые должны были защищать Пандарию.
⠀
⠀
"Вступай в группу вк", переходи по ссылке в шапке ☝

Treccani si occupa di Death Stranding.
Di più, lo fa fare al direttore del VIGAMUS, il Museo del Videogioco. Un'occasione incredibile per rivendicare un minimo di riconoscimento culturale per la nostra forma di intrattenimento preferita.

Peccato che ne venga fuori un pezzo dove i videogiochi vengono costantemente messi a paragone con il cinema. 
Così le ambizioni registiche di Kojima in Death Stranding sono esasperate "complice il coinvolgimento di numerosi attori", poco importa se invece l'idea è che il gameplay sia racconto, non solo raccordo.

Così coinvolgere attori famosi in un videogioco è una "scelta suicida" perché in un videogioco non può emergere la loro personalità, e un game designer non può improvvisarsi regista.

Il Direttore del Museo del Videogioco insomma subordina il videogioco al cinema per buona parte delle 1600 parole dell'articolo.  È l'unico modo per rendere i videogiochi "cultura alta". Se non ci crede nemmeno lui, chi deve crederci?
Beh, noi.

caption.text:
Oddworld viene rilasciato per la prima volta su ps1 nel 1994.il nome deriva dal pianeta in cui è ambientato, circa dieci volte la terra.
Il pianeta è in pericolo e rischia di essere distrutto dalla sua sadica società consumistica e dalle fabbriche. Il personaggio principale è ABE, un alieno impacciato che fa le pulizie in una fabbrica di SNACK.
Quando anche l'ultimo animale fu macellato i proprietari delle fabbriche decisero di macellare piccoli alieni detti mudokon tra cui ABE. Comincia la sua avventura per salvare se stesso e i suoi simili.
Gioco ironico e scavando a fondo ancora attuale e con un pizzico di cinismo.
.
.
RUFY 👒
.
.

DDR4 a 5 GHz e Ryzen 9 3900X: l’overclocker der8auer testa un inedito kit di Gigabyte - L’overclocker Roman “der8auer” Hartung ha messo alla prova su piattaforma X570 con Ryzen 9 3900X un inedito kit di memoria DDR4-5000 di Gigabyte. L’azienda ci sta lavorando internamente da un po’ di tempo, tanto che all’ultima Gamescom di agosto aveva promesso a der8auer che presto gli avrebbe inviato qualcosa di speciale.
Detto, fatto. Il regalo è arrivato e l’overclocker ha ovviamente messo tutto alla prova in un video che potete vedere qui di seguito. I moduli hanno funzionato a 5 GHz senza richiedere particolari interventi o raffreddamento esotici, ma solo l’impostazione di un semplice profilo XMP dal BIOS. Un ulteriore segno che, se ancora avevate dei dubbi, le piattaforme AMD ne hanno fatta di strada dai Ryzen di prima generazione nella compatibilità con le memorie.

I due moduli sono basati su chip Micron, soluzioni DDR4-3200 che di base richiedono 1,2 volt. Per raggiungere 5000 MHz sono necessari 1,55 volt, mentre i timing impostati sono CL18 (18-27-27-38). - Continua a leggere su www.informaticagames.com http://tinyurl.com/y4k37c7g #informaticagames #games #ps4 #playstation4 #gamers #xbox #instagamer #game #nintendo #playstation #xboxone #videogame #gaming #games #gamer #videogames

One of my favourite series's on the PlayStation.

Ryu Ga Gotoku 1 & 2 HD are the Japanese HD ports of the first two Ryu Ga Gotoku games. 
The Ryu Ga Gotoku series is better known in the West by it's Western title name (Yakuza). There are plenty of Ryu Ga Gotoku titles never translated into English including Ryu Ga Gotoku Ishin and Ryu Ga Gotoku Kenzan to name two. 
This collection was never released outside of Japan, although the original two games were released outside of Japan but on the ps2.

Not to be confused with the recent Ryu Ga Gotoku Kiwami/Yakuza Kiwami titles, as they're full remakes whereas this was basically a port.

This collection has no English translation but you can play the original 2 ps2 titles in English.
